413
00:43:35,737 --> 00:43:38,205
mas com tanta raiva.

414
00:43:39,601 --> 00:43:41,510
E juntos nós lutamos
contra um tirano louco.

415
00:43:41,512 --> 00:43:43,645
Bem...

416
00:43:43,647 --> 00:43:45,814
